docs.lead_paragraph: The United States economy on Monday hit a milestone, reaching its longest expansion on record. Just a decade ago, the nation was mired in a severe recession that had erased trillions of dollars in wealth and left millions of people out of work.

headline.print_headline: Minority Women Gained Amid Record Expansion
